<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
<title>Pievra for Agencies - One Platform for Every AI Advertising Protocol</title>
<meta name="description" content="Run AI agent campaigns across AdCP, MCP, UCP, ARTF and A2A from a single platform. Cross-protocol execution, simplified vendor management and unified reporting for agencies."/>
<meta property="og:title" content="Pievra for Agencies - One Platform for Every AI Advertising Protocol"/>
<meta property="og:description" content="Cross-protocol campaign execution, simplified vendor management and unified reporting for agencies."/>
<meta property="og:url" content="https://pievra.com/for-agencies"/>
<meta property="og:type" content="website"/>
<link rel="canonical" href="https://pievra.com/for-agencies"/>

<!-- GA4 Analytics - consent-gated (GDPR/CNIL compliant) -->
<script src="/static/consent.js"></script>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
:root {
  --ink: #0a0e1a;
  --ink-soft: #3d4460;
  --ink-muted: #7a829e;
  --surface: #ffffff;
  --surface-2: #f4f5f9;
  --surface-3: #ebedf5;
  --teal: #00c4a7;
  --teal-dark: #009e86;
  --teal-light: #e0faf6;
  --border: #e2e4ed;
  --radius: 12px;
  --radius-lg: 20px;
  --shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(10,14,26,0.08);
  --shadow-lg: 0 12px 48px rgba(10,14,26,0.14);
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  background: var(--surface);
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: 1.6;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}
h1,h2,h3,h4,h5 { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; line-height: 1.15; }

/* NAV */
nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  height: 64px;
}
.nav-inner {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px;
  height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
}
.nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; text-decoration: none; }
.logo-mark {
  width: 36px; height: 36px; background: var(--ink);
  border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 18px;
}
.logo-text { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 20px; color: var(--ink); }
.nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 32px; }
.nav-links a {
  font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-soft);
  text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;
}
.nav-links a:hover { color: var(--ink); }
.nav-cta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
.btn-ghost {
  padding: 8px 16px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--ink-soft); background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  border-radius: 8px; transition: background 0.2s; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--surface-2); }
.btn-primary {
  padding: 8px 20px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
  color: white; background: var(--ink); border: none; cursor: pointer;
  border-radius: 8px; transition: all 0.2s; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: #1a2035; transform: translateY(-1px); }

/* HERO */
.hero {
  padding: 140px 24px 80px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% -10%, rgba(0,196,167,0.10) 0%, transparent 70%);
}
.hero-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
.hero-pill {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px;
  background: var(--surface-2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.hero-pill .dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--teal); animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
@keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)} 50%{opacity:0.6;transform:scale(1.3)} }
.hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(38px, 5.5vw, 72px); font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -2px; margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.hero h1 .accent { color: var(--teal); }
.hero-sub {
  font-size: 18px; color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 620px;
  margin: 0 auto 40px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.7;
}
.hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.btn-teal {
  padding: 14px 28px; background: var(--teal); color: white;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;
  border: none; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; text-decoration: none;
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
}
.btn-teal:hover { background: var(--teal-dark); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,196,167,0.3); }
.btn-outline {
  padding: 14px 28px; background: transparent; color: var(--ink);
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;
  border: 2px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; text-decoration: none;
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
}
.btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--ink); transform: translateY(-2px); }

/* SECTIONS */
.section { padding: 96px 24px; }
.section-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
.section-tag { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--teal); margin-bottom: 12px; }
.section-title { font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 46px); font-weight: 800; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.section-sub { font-size: 17px; color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 560px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 56px; }
.section-alt { background: var(--surface-2); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }

/* VALUE PROPS */
.value-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
.value-card {
  border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 32px; background: white; transition: all 0.25s;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.value-card::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
  background: var(--teal); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s;
}
.value-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); transform: translateY(-3px); }
.value-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
.value-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: block; }
.value-title { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 12px; }
.value-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.7; }

/* HOW IT WORKS */
.how-steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 32px; position: relative; }
.how-steps::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: 28px; left: 15%; right: 15%; height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--teal), transparent);
}
.how-step { text-align: center; position: relative; }
.step-num {
  width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--ink); color: var(--teal);
  font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  margin: 0 auto 20px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
}
.step-title { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.step-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.6; }

/* INTEGRATION */
.integration-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; align-items: start; }
.integration-copy h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.integration-copy p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.checklist { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
.checklist li {
  font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500;
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; line-height: 1.6;
}
.check-icon {
  width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--teal-light);
  border: 1px solid var(--teal); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--teal-dark); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;
}
.info-cards { display: grid; gap: 14px; }
.info-card {
  background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 20px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
}
.info-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
.info-card-icon {
  width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px; background: var(--surface-2);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.info-card h4 { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.info-card p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.5; }

/* CTA BANNER */
.cta-banner {
  background: var(--ink); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 64px 48px; text-align: center; color: white;
}
.cta-banner h2 {
  font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 40px); font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.cta-banner p {
  font-size: 17px; color: #8892b0; max-width: 500px;
  margin: 0 auto 36px; line-height: 1.7;
}
.cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

/* FOOTER */
footer {
  background: #060810; color: #4a5270;
  border-top: 1px solid #0e1220; padding: 64px 24px 40px;
}
.footer-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
.footer-top { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
.footer-brand p { font-size: 13px; color: #4a5270; line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 12px; max-width: 220px; }
.footer-col h4 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #8892b0; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
.footer-col ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
.footer-col ul li a { font-size: 13px; color: #4a5270; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
.footer-col ul li a:hover { color: var(--teal); }
.footer-bottom {
  border-top: 1px solid #0e1220; padding-top: 28px;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
}
.footer-bottom p { font-size: 13px; }

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .value-cards, .how-steps, .integration-grid, .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .how-steps::before { display: none; }
  .nav-links { display: none; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav style="background:#0a0e1a;height:60px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 40px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100">
  <a href="/" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;text-decoration:none">
    <div style="width:30px;height:30px;background:#00c4a7;border-radius:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:Manrope,sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:14px;color:#0a0e1a">P</div>
    <div style="font-family:Manrope,sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:16px;color:#fff">pievra</div>
  </a>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:center">
    <a href="/marketplace" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500">Marketplace</a>
    <a href="/partners" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500">Partners</a>
    <a href="/news" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500">News</a>
    <a href="/careers" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500">Careers</a>
    <a href="/signin" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:500">Sign In</a>
    <a href="/signup" style="background:#00c4a7;color:#0a0e1a;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none">Sign Up Free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-pill"><span class="dot"></span> For Agencies</div>
    <h1>One platform for every<br><span class="accent">AI advertising protocol</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Stop managing separate integrations for AdCP, MCP, UCP, ARTF and A2A. Pievra gives your agency a single orchestration layer to plan, execute and report across all agentic advertising protocols.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/signup" class="btn-teal">Sign Up Free</a>
      <a href="/request-demo" class="btn-outline">Request Demo</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VALUE PROPS -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-tag">Why Agencies Choose Pievra</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Simplify multi-protocol campaign management</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Each AI advertising protocol has its own spec, agent format and auction logic. Pievra normalises them into one workflow.</p>

    <div class="value-cards">
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-icon">&#x1F310;</span>
        <h3 class="value-title">Cross-Protocol Execution</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">Define a campaign once and Pievra translates it into the correct format for each protocol. Run AdCP, MCP, UCP, ARTF and A2A campaigns from a single brief without rebuilding assets per spec.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-icon">&#x1F4CB;</span>
        <h3 class="value-title">Simplified Vendor Management</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">One contract, one integration, one billing relationship. Instead of onboarding each protocol vendor separately, access the full agent marketplace through Pievra's unified layer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-icon">&#x1F4CA;</span>
        <h3 class="value-title">Unified Reporting</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">See delivery, spend and agent activity across all protocols in a single dashboard. Compare protocol performance side by side without exporting data from five different systems.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-tag">How It Works</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three steps to multi-protocol campaigns</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">From brief to live execution across every protocol your clients need.</p>

    <div class="how-steps">
      <div class="how-step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Define Your Campaign</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">Set your targeting, budget, KPIs and creative parameters in Pievra's campaign planner. One brief covers all protocols.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Pievra Matches Agents</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">The platform identifies compatible agents across AdCP, MCP, UCP, ARTF and A2A, then routes your campaign to the right protocol endpoints.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Monitor from One Dashboard</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">Track delivery, agent responses and spend in real time. All protocol data is normalised into a single reporting view for your team and clients.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INTEGRATION / GETTING STARTED -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="integration-grid">
      <div class="integration-copy">
        <p class="section-tag">Getting Started</p>
        <h2>How agencies integrate with Pievra</h2>
        <p>Pievra is designed for agency workflows. No protocol expertise required to get started.</p>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li><span class="check-icon">&#x2713;</span> Create your agency workspace and invite team members</li>
          <li><span class="check-icon">&#x2713;</span> Connect your existing DSP accounts or use Pievra's agent marketplace</li>
          <li><span class="check-icon">&#x2713;</span> Build campaigns using the visual planner or the REST API</li>
          <li><span class="check-icon">&#x2713;</span> Set protocol preferences or let Pievra auto-select based on campaign goals</li>
          <li><span class="check-icon">&#x2713;</span> Go live and monitor from the unified dashboard</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn-teal">Sign Up Free</a>
      </div>
      <div class="info-cards">
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-card-icon">&#x1F4E6;</div>
          <div>
            <h4>REST API & SDKs</h4>
            <p>Programmatic access for agencies that want to integrate Pievra into existing tools and internal platforms.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-card-icon">&#x1F465;</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Team Workspaces</h4>
            <p>Invite strategists, traders and analysts with role-based access. Each team member sees the data relevant to their role.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-card-icon">&#x1F4C4;</div>
          <div>
            <h4>White-Label Reporting</h4>
            <p>Generate client-ready reports with your agency branding. Export as PDF or share via live dashboard links.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-card-icon">&#x1F527;</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Onboarding Support</h4>
            <p>Free onboarding resources and community support. We help your team understand all five protocols.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="cta-banner">
      <h2>Ready to simplify multi-protocol advertising?</h2>
      <p>Manage AI agent campaigns across every protocol from one platform. Free to use, no credit card required.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="/signup" class="btn-teal">Sign Up Free</a>
        <a href="/request-demo" class="btn-outline" style="color:white;border-color:#2a3050">Request Demo</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-top">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px">
          <div class="logo-mark">&#x1F419;</div>
          <span style="font-family:'Manrope',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:18px;color:white">pievra</span>
        </div>
        <p>Eight arms. Every AI agent protocol. The protocol-neutral orchestration layer for programmatic advertising.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Platform</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/for-agencies">For Agencies</a></li>
          <li><a href="/for-brands">For Brands</a></li>
          <li><a href="/for-publishers">For Publishers</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Resources</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/pievra">Docs</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/pievra">GitHub</a></li>
          <li><a href="/news">Protocol News</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Legal</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/privacy">Privacy & GDPR</a></li>
          <li><a href="/terms">Terms & Conditions</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Pievra. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:16px">
        <a href="https://github.com/pievra" target="_blank" style="color:#4a5270;text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.2s" onmouseover="this.style.color='#00c4a7'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#4a5270'">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/pievra" target="_blank" style="color:#4a5270;text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.2s" onmouseover="this.style.color='#00c4a7'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#4a5270'">Twitter/X</a>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/pievra" target="_blank" style="color:#4a5270;text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.2s" onmouseover="this.style.color='#00c4a7'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#4a5270'">Discord</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
  const nav = document.querySelector('nav');
  nav.style.boxShadow = window.scrollY > 20 ? '0 2px 20px rgba(10,14,26,0.08)' : 'none';
});
</script>

</body>
</html>